{"service_name": "Cloud-based ERP and CRM solutions consultancy", "service_id": "4651601767694336", "company_name": "Medley Business Solutions Ltd", "page_content": "<main id=\"content\" role=\"main\">\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <header class=\"page-heading-smaller\">\n    <p class=\"context\">\n     Medley Business Solutions Ltd\n    </p>\n    <h1>\n     Cloud-based ERP and CRM solutions consultancy\n    </h1>\n   </header>\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <p class=\"service-summary-lede\">\n    Medley supports each stage of the evaluation, specification, selection, procurement and roll-out of ERP and CRM cloud solutions. \r\n\r\nMany organisations are reviewing their ERP and CRM solutions which have been heavily customised over many years. They need a lower cost solution that can support the changing needs of the business.\n   </p>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Features\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Current situation review, options development and requirements analysis\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Business process analysis, improvement options and facilitated workshops\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     High-level, outline and detailed business case development\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Development of the procurement approach and procurement management\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Market, supplier, service and product review and evaluation\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     ERP and CRM cloud solution evaluation and selection\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Commercial requirements and RFI, RFQ, ITT preparation\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Market engagement and demonstration, supplier response evaluation and scoring criteria\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Service review and specification, transition planning and roll-out management\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Proof of concept and pilot\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Benefits\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Well executed evaluation, procurement and roll-out process\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Focus on commercial, business, technical and people aspects\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     MEAT \u2013 Most economical advantageous tender and solution\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Rapid engagement with the most appropriate suppliers\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     ERP components evaluated include HR, Procurement, Finance, Accounts, Projects, Inventory\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Fully auditable procurement process\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Minimise the cost of transition to new solutions\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Reduced ERP or CRM support and enhancement costs\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     A solution that can accommodate future changes to the business\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Access to independent Medley ERP and CRM expertise\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"column-one-third\">\n   <div id=\"meta\">\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Pricing\n    </h2>\n    <p class=\"price\">\n     \u00a3647 to \u00a31087 per person per day\n    </p>\n    <ul class=\"price-caveats\">\n     <li>\n      Excluding VAT\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Minimum contract period: Hour\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Service documents\n    </h2>\n    <ul class=\"document-list\">\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/92442/4651601767694336-pricing-document.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Pricing\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/92442/4651601767694336-sfia-rate-card.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       SFIA rate card\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/92442/4651601767694336-service-definition-document.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Service definition\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/documents/92442/4651601767694336-terms-and-conditions.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Terms and conditions\n      </a>\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"sidebar-heading\">\n     Framework\n    </h2>\n    <div class=\"external-link-default\">\n     <a href=\"http://ccs-agreements.cabinetoffice.gov.uk/contracts/rm1557vi\" rel=\"external\">\n      G-Cloud 6\n     </a>\n    </div>\n    <h2 class=\"sidebar-heading\">\n     Service ID\n    </h2>\n    <div class=\"service-id\">\n     <span class=\"service-id-chunk\">\n      4651\n     </span>\n     <span class=\"service-id-chunk\">\n      6017\n     </span>\n     <span class=\"service-id-chunk\">\n      6769\n     </span>\n     <span class=\"service-id-chunk\">\n      4336\n     </span>\n    </div>\n    <h2 class=\"sidebar-heading\">\n     Contact\n    </h2>\n    <div class=\"contact-details\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/Organization\">\n     <p class=\"contact-details-organisation\">\n      <span itemprop=\"name\">\n       Medley Business Solutions Ltd\n      </span>\n     </p>\n     <p class=\"contact-details-block\">\n      <span itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/Person\">\n       <span itemprop=\"name\">\n        TIM EGLEN\n       </span>\n    